    {
      "name": "cleanup_envelope_chunks",
      "docs": [
        "Permissionless reaper for `EnvelopeChunks` PDAs an operator started",
        "but never finished. Callable once the chain has advanced past",
        "`epoch_index` (consensus reached); rent returns to the original",
        "uploader. The caller pays only the tx fee."
      ],
      "discriminator": [
        224,
        118,
        156,
        99,
        9,
        136,
        14,
        207
      ],
      "accounts": [
        {
          "name": "reaper",
          "docs": [
            "Anyone can invoke. Pays the tx fee, gets nothing in return."
          ],
          "signer": true
        },
        {
          "name": "config"
        },
        {
          "name": "latest_outbound_envelope"
        },
        {
          "name": "chunk_buffer",
          "docs": [
            "The stale buffer to close. The seeds constraint pins the PDA's",
            "third seed to `uploader.key()`, so Anchor's PDA derivation is",
            "itself the proof that `uploader` IS the operator that originally",
            "opened this buffer. `close = uploader` returns rent to that key."
          ],
          "writable": true
        },
        {
          "name": "uploader",
          "docs": [
            "The original uploader. Receives the reclaimed rent. Must be `mut`",
            "so Anchor's `close` can credit lamports."
          ],
          "writable": true
        }
      ],
